# get_irida_download_sequence_file
# download a paired-end sequence file from a sample
# PROJECT_ID is used only for tab completion, not passed to the API
# SAMPLE_ID, PAIR_ID, FILE_ID are used in the curl call
# filename is taken from the JSON metadata before downloading
#
# NOTE: get_irida_download_sequence_pair downloads both R1 and R2 in one call.
#
# example: get_irida_download_sequence_file [TAB once for project id] 2:Test_Data_Uploading [TAB again for sample id] 3:sample-1-Added [TAB again for pair id] 3 [TAB again for file id] 5
#
